text:
G'day!

I have installed ActiveState Pel 5.6.1. And I try to implement a content filter 
by using perl. When executing following perl code the request will hang:

while (<STDIN>) {
  $_ =~ s/foo/bar/gi;
  print $_
}
exit (0);

It seems as if the while loop does not get false. Any idea why this happens? 
Solutions to solve this problem?

Regards Jan
